# VHS tape for escpod inspect command
Output docs/images/inspect.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontFamily "Source Code Pro"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 600
Set LetterSpacing 0
Set LineHeight 1.2
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Margin 20
Set BorderRadius 10

Type "escpod inspect summary data/drna/yeast_trna_reads.pod5"
Enter
Sleep 5s
